で，この関数は条件がtrueのとき白，falseのとき黒を座標 (z, M) に描画する．ここでは条件が z-M > 0，すなわち z > M になっているので，z座標の値 > M座標の値 ならば黒が描画される．

column2: In the function λx.x, "x" is called a bound variable because it is both in the body of the function and a parameter.
In λx.y, "y" is called a free variable because it is never declared before hand
(λx.λy.λz.xyz) is equivalent to f(x, y, z) = ((x y) z)
Sometimes λxy.<body> is used interchangeably with: λx.λy.<body>

column2: First, we can define an "if" function λbtf that returns t if b is True and f if b is False
IF is equivalent to: λb.λt.λf.b t f
a AND b is equivalent to: λab.IF a b F
a OR b is equivalent to: λab.IF a T b
